data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful unit on Fiesta Key complete with resort-style amenities! This bright townhome features 4 beds and 3.5 bathrooms, with 2 of the bedrooms being master suites. One master bedroom is located on the main floor, while the other is on the second floor. Both are spacious and have private bathrooms. The interior is modern and stylish, with meticulous detailing throughout. Modern lighting, kitchen island with power outlets, and sliding glass door, accentuate the living/dining combo. Walking through the glass door will take you to the screened-in courtyard at the rear of the property; Enjoy the natural light and a glass of your favorite beverage, and take a walk around the pond, clear if you prefer to move around. Luckily for you, this townhome is a final unit and that means you're one of the few with a balcony. The second floor takes you to your balcony and offers a pristine view and a great place to relax. This amazing unit with 2 parking spots, is the perfect home for you and your family, but can also be a great investment property. Any renter is sure to love it for the same reasons you do! Does the set have resort-style amenities included? Fiesta Key allows you to enjoy a clubhouse, swimming pool, tennis court, and fitness center! Belcome  Primary residence, vacation home, or long rental and short-term rental. Everything from restaurants to shopping malls, healthcare to entertainment, is nearby. Disney 15 minutes away, Universal Studios and SeaWorld are only 20 or 30 minutes away. Easy access to many attractions, restaurants, shopping, sun rail. New flooring and new paint throughout. Call, text, or WhatsApp for your appointment today and see for yourself before it's over!
